		{
			dependencies: ["5E18F03C7637CC27"]
			description: ["Netherite is obtained by smithing Diamond armor with Netherite Ingots — themselves smelted from Ancient Debris mined in the lower Nether. The resulting set is the strongest vanilla armor in the game: knockback resistant, fire immune, and it floats in lava. It will carry you comfortably through the mid-game until dedicated magical and GT armor paths take over."]
