		{
			description: ["Armor in this pack comes from several distinct paths. Tinkers Construct is tools only: it provides no armor and no weapons — Spartan Weaponry and Iron's Spells fill those roles. For armor: the Physical path runs Diamond to Netherite to GTCEu plate sets (rubber, bronze, steel, and higher alloys). The Soul path runs Jade Silk and soul-enhanced sets for cultivators. The Mine and Slash system applies stat souls to any armor base you are already wearing — it does not provide its own armor pieces. Build your armor base first on whichever path fits your playstyle, then layer MnS souls on top to close the gaps."]
			id: "AR01000000000001"
			rewards: [
				{
					auto: "enabled"
					command: "/mine_and_slash give xp_times_lvl @p 100"
					elevate_perms: true
