		{
			dependencies: ["AR01000000000001"]
			description: ["GTCEu Rubber Plate armor is the first step into technology-based protection. Rubber plates are produced from Natural Rubber fluid in the Fluid Solidifier, then pressed into plates and formed into armor at the crafting table. Rubber armor provides reasonable physical defense with one notable property: electrical insulation. It is the recommended armor base when working extensively around GTCEu machines and power cables, as it protects against stray voltage damage. Craft the full set before building out your first LV machine room."]
			id: "AR01000000000002"
