		{
			dependencies: ["AR01000000000002"]
			description: ["Bronze Plate armor is the first metallic GTCEu armor tier. Bronze plates are alloyed from tin and copper in the Alloy Smelter or via the Chemical Bath, then formed into armor. Bronze armor provides substantially better defense than rubber and holds up comfortably through the early GT progression. Combine a Bronze set with Common or Uncommon MnS armor souls for a reliable baseline before Steel becomes available in the EBF."]
			id: "AR01000000000003"
