		{
			dependencies: ["AR01000000000003"]
			description: ["Steel Plate armor is the GT benchmark for mid-game survival. Steel plates require steel ingots — produced in the Electric Blast Furnace at 1000 K minimum — formed into plates via the Plate Bending Machine. A full Steel Plate set combined with Rare or Epic MnS armor souls provides strong defense well into IV-tier GTCEu content. Steel is the armor baseline to maintain until Tungstensteel and higher GT alloys become practical replacements at LuV and above."]
