		{
			dependencies: ["AR01000000000004"]
			description: ["Aluminium Plate armor is the first post-Steel milestone in the GTCEu armor track. Aluminium ingots are produced in the Electrolyzer from Bauxite dust, then pressed into plates in the Plate Bending Machine. The resulting set is lighter than steel with comparable defense and a cleaner smelting path — no EBF temperature gating beyond what Steel already required. Pair with Rare or Epic MnS armor souls for a reliable set that carries you through EV-tier GTCEu content."]
			id: "AR01000000000005"
