		{
			dependencies: ["AR01000000000005"]
			description: ["Titanium Plate armor represents the upper boundary of the GTCEu plate armor track. Titanium requires the Electric Blast Furnace at 1941 K and access to Rutile or Ilmenite ore — both found in high-tier ore veins. The plates are expensive to produce but the resulting armor is among the strongest non-magical sets available. A full Titanium set with Epic or Legendary MnS armor souls is the recommended armor loadout entering IV-tier GTCEu and late-game dimensional content."]
			id: "AR01000000000006"
