			dependencies: ["AR01000000000006", "484E4A14F94A2FA8", "36285B3BA9B195F6"]
			description: ["Three armor paths, fully realized. The GTCEu plate track ended at Titanium, your MnS armor souls are Legendary grade, and you understand what Jade Silk is for. From here, the remaining armor upgrades — Tungstensteel and higher GT alloys, Mythic MnS souls, and late-game magical sets — are refinements rather than unlocks. Continue into the endgame with a loadout that covers every defense category."]
